": 0, "vbr": 2887.205, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 44847677, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-2627923477557974v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by maryisalien", "description": "repetition compulsion 🍒", "duration": 124.266, "timestamp": 1765839534, "uploader_id": "4232731761", "uploader": "Mary Allison", "channel": "maryisalien", "like_count": 102109, "comment_count": 4577, "comments": [{"author": "madelynnlm", "author_id": "254165352", "id": "18428280694188754", "text": "SYNCHRONICITIESSSSSSSS ꩜", "timestamp": 1775151394}, {"author": "heartwood_go", "author_id": "9263542257", "id": "18158906275440958", "text": "Makes perfect sense. The only question is whether there are two outcomes and part of humanity goes one way and the other part goes another. Multiple timelines/dimensions/etc.", "timestamp": 1775050869}, {"author": "forster7484", "author_id": "10483111111", "id": "18084914918592735", "text": "We have Freewill ❤️\nWe can  increase our vibration energy and frequency by raising our LOVE .\nOur Divide Code the Fibonacci  Sequence is within us all and nature .\nWe have a  God given Power within us all once we let go of Fear and connect to our source our creator our God❤️\n\n❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️\nLove to everyone in the world ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1774951088}, {"author": "tasha.lyn.nette", "author_id": "6815633586", "id": "18428567773186511", "text": "Y'all are awakening because Charlie kirk was killed? 🙃", "timestamp": 1774946356}, {"author": "vog.og.sg", "author_id": "4339726593", "id": "18015731447831346", "text": "100% heading towards suppression", "timestamp": 1774905804}, {"author": "__heykirby", "author_id": "12822217", "id": "18015761324831671", "text": "I’m AuDHD and I recognized and voiced the inconsistencies immediately (pattern recognition 🤌) and I’m realizing I should keep my mouth shut for a lil longer because people think I’m absolutely schizolevel insane for years til they learn …but I still never hear from them again because the NT ego is just cooked. \n\nI’m learning I think? \n\nOr being further traumatized and being pushed back into masking idfk", "timestamp": 1774879680}, {"author": "aby.smal", "author_id": "3426093951", "id": "18318275479271783", "text": "What has been done shall be done and there is no new thing under the sun. Get ready for the next reset. After 100 years history changes because everyone died that lived through it. Proof? Find really old history books that are over 100 years old. I have 5 of them.", "timestamp": 1774879651}, {"author": "eden_agm___", "author_id": "360910991", "id": "18166415116420095", "text": "I always like to think that the book of revelations is basically this. What we are watching in our world, it will reveal us somehow the truth with hard events but it will be the end of those dark times. I go towards that side.", "timestamp": 1774851196}, {"author": "brandi_nichole84", "author_id": "11707098", "id": "18100511966298875", "text": "Sadly I believe suppression 😞 yes, there’s more good than bad. However, the amount of evil walking this earth that control everything id overwhelming.", "timestamp": 1774836193}, {"author": "jesus_is_not_judaism", "author_id": "7913213723", "id": "18139856347449048", "text": "The link I am sharing is some young people who have noticed that the same person who purchased the World Trade Center towers just purchased a tower in LA.  https://www.facebook.com/share/1JBMmnuHCv/?mibextid=wwXIfr", "timestamp": 1774834078}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/601211220_18421036630139762_9045133474210949601_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p640x640_tt6&e